Package com.pandora.general.objects

Class AbstractBaseObject

java.lang.Object
com.pandora.general.objects.AbstractBaseObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
Cell, CellTimestep, River, RiverTimestep
public abstract class AbstractBaseObject extends Object
The AbstractBaseObject is an abstract class providing a base structure for objects with a unique identifier (id) and a name. It includes standard getter and setter methods for accessing and modifying the identifier and name.

This class uses the Lombok library annotations Getter, Setter, NoArgsConstructor, and SuperBuilder to automatically generate getter and setter methods, a no-args constructor, and a builder.
